    "Text": "\n    <p>BIND (Berkeley Internet Name Domain) is a Name Server.</p>\n  "
  },
  "Description": {
    "Text": "\n    <p>Multiple vulnerabilities have been discovered in BIND. Please review the\n      CVE identifiers referenced below for details.\n    </p>\n  "
  },
